# Times table quiz: Practice multiplication
remember num = random 2 12
remember multiplier = random 1 12
remember correct = num * multiplier
remember answer = 0
print "QUIZ TIME!"
print "What is " num " x " multiplier "?"
ask "Your answer: " answer
if answer is correct
  print "Correct! " num " x " multiplier " = " correct
else
  print "Oops! The answer is " correct
  print "You said " answer ". Try again next time!"


